---
const siteTitle = "THE SEGMENTED NERD";
const currentStatus = "SYSTEMS_ONLINE";
---
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>{siteTitle}</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root { --green: #00ff41; --bg: #0a0a0a; --card: #141414; --border: #222; --text: #a0a0a0; }
        body { background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; margin: 0; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; min-height: 100vh; }
        .dashboard { width: 100%; max-width: 1000px; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid var(--border); background: #0f0f0f; position: relative; }
        .header { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-bottom: 15px; margin-bottom: 30px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
        h1 { color: var(--green); margin: 0; font-size: 1.2rem; letter-spacing: 3px; font-weight: 700; }
        .status { font-size: 0.7rem; background: rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.1); color: var(--green); padding: 4px 8px; border: 1px solid var(--green); border-radius: 3px; }
        .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; }
        .card { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 20px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
        .card::before { content: ""; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 3px; height: 100%; background: var(--border); transition: background 0.3s; }
        .card:hover::before { background: var(--green); }
        .card:hover { border-color: #333; }
        h2 { color: #fff; font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0 0 10px 0; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        p { font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0 0 15px 0; }
        .tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; }
        .tag { font-size: 0.65rem; color: #666; border: 1px solid #333; padding: 2px 6px; }
        footer { margin-top: 40px; font-size: 0.7rem; color: #444; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 10px; text-align: right; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="dashboard">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>{siteTitle}</h1>
            <div class="status">{currentStatus}</div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card">
                <h2>01 // FIELD NOTES</h2>
                <p>Enterprise virtualization, VCF stack architecture, and distributed security implementation.</p>
                <div class="tags">
                    <span class="tag">#VDEFEND</span><span class="tag">#NSX</span><span class="tag">#ZERO_TRUST</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h2>02 // THE SHOP</h2>
                <p>Custom woodworking projects. 1x4 builds, Lego displays, and shop organization.</p>
                <div class="tags">
                    <span class="tag">#WOODWORKING</span><span class="tag">#FURNITURE</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h2>03 // THE LAB</h2>
                <p>Functional 3D printing for household and shop efficiency using PETG-CF and Nylon.</p>
                <div class="tags">
                    <span class="tag">#BAMBU_LAB</span><span class="tag">#3D_PRINTING</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h2>04 // THE FLEET</h2>
                <p>Maintenance and DIY logs for the 2019 F-350 Diesel and 2020 Sequoia TRD Pro.</p>
                <div class="tags">
                    <span class="tag">#6.7L_POWERSTROKE</span><span class="tag">#TOYOTA_TRD</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <footer>
            &copy; 2026 // JOSHUA D. GREEN // STAFF TECHNICAL ADOPTION MANAGER
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
